This paper is about reinforcement learning with a focus on AI safety, which is a topic that falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of human input in the learning process, which is a common theme in machine learning (cs.LG) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also mentions the use of policies in new environments, which is relevant to robotics (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY).
